    <main>
      <section id="bg-about" class="max-h-[550px] h-[550px] flex items-center">
        <div class="text-white font-bold w-[86%] m-auto text-5xl">
          <h1>Get to know us...</h1>
        </div>
      </section>

      <article class="w-[86%] m-auto my-12 text-xl">
        <p>
          We believe that the hostel allocation industry in KWASU is broken, and
          that many students resignedly accept bad services from greedy
          landlords, caretakers and agents because...well, what can they do?
          This state of the hostel market forces students to pay more, even as
          many of these hostel providers offer the most mediocre experience they
          can get away with. And so, a economy that punishes the students is
          established. Homely is our redesign of the housing and allocation
          industry. We're building an efficient world where students get
          hostels, not just the bare facilities, but comfortable and well
          structured rooms, with no friction, by our highly trained service
          providers. No more expensive but poorly structured hostels. We’re here
          now, and we’ve got you.
        </p>
      </article>
